{"lastModified":1771253353034,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::98b07ef0-37b4-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e","yachtType":["Catamaran","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nWelcome aboard the Nautitech 46 Fly, a reliable catamaran constructed in 2017 and currently moored at Alimos Marina, Greece. Designed to accommodate up to 10 guests in style, this luxurious vessel features four double cabins with ensuite WC, along with two single cabins for the crew, ensuring ample space for everyone. The spacious saloon and kitchen provide a comfortable gathering area for relaxation and dining.\n\nSail confidently knowing that your needs are well taken care of aboard the Nautitech 46 Fly, ensuring a smooth and enjoyable journey along the picturesque Greek coastline.\n\nEquipped with a generator, Watermaker, A/C, and heating, this catamaran ensures comfort in all weather conditions. Enjoy entertainment with the audio system and outside speakers, while the bimini and solar panels offer shade and sustainable energy solutions. The flybridge provides an elevated vantage point for breathtaking views.\n\nIndulge in culinary delights with the fully-equipped galley, featuring a coffee machine, oven, cooker, sink, and kitchen utensils, allowing you to prepare delicious meals while on board.","blueprint":{"name":"AURELIANO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::98b07ef0-37b4-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::c9cabd70-37b9-11f0-9b25-9f7dde17423b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::98b07ef0-37b4-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::355de9f0-37b9-11f0-9b24-9f7dde17423b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::98b07ef0-37b4-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::355d26a0-37b9-11f0-9b24-9f7dde17423b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::98b07ef0-37b4-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::355f2270-37b9-11f0-9b24-9f7dde17423b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::98b07ef0-37b4-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::355f4980-37b9-11f0-9b24-9f7dde17423b/{imageVariant}","/med